{"id": "1364553167936819301", "channel_id": "1364553167936819301", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "感謝各位守密人的支持！\n《忘卻前夜》OST：奧吉爾EP·無愧榮光，今日發佈～歡迎大家收聽、下載及分享～如果有基於OST的二次創作，也歡迎分享給我們！ （二創請遵照同人規則，OST內容請勿商用）\n\n忘卻前夜OST：奧吉爾EP·無愧榮光\n那個身量尚且不如長槍的年輕騎士，無愧於對公主宣誓時許下的每一句誓言。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n規劃：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\n《Morimens》OST：《Ogier EP· Worthy of the Glory》 was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\n《Morimens》OST：《Ogier EP· Worthy of the Glory》 \nThe young knight, whose stature was not even as tall as the lance, lived up to every word of the oath he made to the princess.\n\nComposer：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n\nPlanning：B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2025-04-23T10:47:07.408000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍩", "emoji_id": null, "count": 9}], "attachments": [{"id": "1364553169065218181", "filename": "-.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 4948830, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1364553167936819301/1364553169065218181/-.png?ex=69ccf7ab&is=69cba62b&hm=5fc58f4fcd7e63ec5ad1808667e0853a0986b20dbe6ca39235c45fead5c41df4&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1364553167936819301", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：奧吉爾EP·無愧榮光", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1364553305199743011", "channel_id": "1364553167936819301", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**01.幼犬訓練-Of Pups and Squires-**\n\n忠誠而勇敢的狗狗會自己制定訓練的計劃，而撫慰一切傷心與疲憊，只需要你一個鼓勵的目光。\nThe loyal and brave dog will make his own training plan, and to soothe all the sadness and fatigue, all he needs is an encouraging look from you.", "timestamp": "2025-04-23T10:47:40.134000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1364553304662736909", "filename": "1.-Of_Pups_and_Squires-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 22552704, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1364553167936819301/1364553304662736909/1.-Of_Pups_and_Squires-.wav?ex=69ccf7cc&is=69cba64c&hm=77c3954d79c2e5cee7d5545587a74bf31b509f351ee509cba1961987d402920a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1364553167936819301", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：奧吉爾EP·無愧榮光", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1364553398707556414", "channel_id": "1364553167936819301", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**02.宮廷春日宴-Courtly Spring Feast-**\n\n春日的暖陽、夢幻的宮殿、旋轉的禮裙、充滿歡笑的舞會，以及美麗又溫柔的公主。\n這些就是騎士想要守護的全部。\nThe warm spring sun, the dreamy palace, the spinning dress, the ball full of laughter, and the beautiful and gentle princess.\nThese are all the knight wants to protect.", "timestamp": "2025-04-23T10:48:02.428000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1364553398589853746", "filename": "2.-Courtly_Spring_Feast-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 27629016, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1364553167936819301/1364553398589853746/2.-Courtly_Spring_Feast-.wav?ex=69ccf7e2&is=69cba662&hm=8aaad8d4e7027f259c039624b6d97c576a066eef28d45648c6af9f18e80023e7&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1364553167936819301", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：奧吉爾EP·無愧榮光", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
